<p>Our first Virtual Practicum in Bioluminescence was held from late February to early April 2021 and we were honored to host 16 students from colleges and universities across the United States and Spain: Boston University, Carleton College, College of William & Mary, Hunter College, Michigan State University, New York University, Northeastern University, Universidad CEU San Pablo, Madrid, University of California, Los Angeles, University of Colorado Boulder, University of Kentucky, University of Nevada, Las Vegas, University of Oklahoma, University of Puerto Rico, Cayey, University of Puerto Rico, Río Piedras, and the University of Rochester.</p>
