<p>After participating in lectures and discussion sections, the students were met with the challenge of our Shark Tank competition. It was as fierce and popular as ever, and the students impressed us with their thoughtful, well-researched pitches.</p>
<br>
<p>Whether near or far, our team has an absolute blast meeting and working with our Practicum students!</p>
